<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language>英文</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:44:52 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Microsoft is no longer making new games for the Xbox One]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在 Xbox Series X/S 生命周期将近三年后，微软表示不再为<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/xbox-one/">Xbox One</a>制作游戏。虽然该公司将继续支持正在进行的上一代游戏，如<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/minecraft/"><em>Minecraft</em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/halo-infinite/"><em>Halo Infinite</em></a> ，但没有 Xbox Game Studios 团队正在为旧游戏机开发新游戏。 “我们已经转向第 9 代，”Xbox 游戏工作室负责人 Matt Booty 告诉<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.axios.com/2023/06/15/xbox-game-studios-matt-booty"><em>Axios</em></a> ，他指的是 Xbox Series X/S 游戏机。该公司还制作 PC 游戏。</p><p>这一举措必须在某个时候发生，以避免更新和更复杂的游戏因已有十年历史的 Xbox One 的硬件限制而受到阻碍。尽管如此，那些坚持使用 Xbox One 的人仍有可能通过<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-cloud-gaming-beta-180329068.html">Xbox 云游戏</a>玩<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/starfield/"><em>Starfield</em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/forza-motorsport-wants-you-to-drive-forever-183033371.html"><em>Forza Motorsport</em></a>等系列 X/S 游戏。 “这就是我们要维持支持的方式，”Booty 说。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这一消息是在 Xbox 在上周末的大型年度展示会上大放异彩之后发布的。它宣布了新的标题，例如 Compulsion 的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/south-of-midnight-is-a-southern-gothic-monster-adventure-from-compulsion-games-173100633.html"><em>《午夜以南》</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em>和 InXile 的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/clockwork-revolution-is-a-time-traveling-rpg-of-steampunk-anarchy-183507054.html"><em>Clockwork Revolution</em></a> ，同时提供<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/take-a-peek-at-xboxs-fable-reboot-in-action-172438277.html"><em>Fable</em></a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/obsidian-fantasy-rpg-avowed-release-date-sgf-2023-174259416.html"><em>Avowed</em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/senuas-saga-hellblade-ii-will-arrive-in-2024-175240445.html"><em>Senua&#39;s Saga：Hellblade II 等</em></a>游戏的全新外观。</p><p>离开 Xbox One 将使微软的团队摆脱上一代产品的束缚。然而，一些第三方开发者<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/developer-claims-many-studios-are-asking-xbox-to-drop-mandatory-series-s-compatibility/">担心</a>，功能不如 X 系列的 Xbox Series S 也会阻碍他们的发展。</p><p> Booty 承认要确保游戏在 Series S 上运行良好需要“更多工作”。不过，他指出微软的工作室（尤其是那些为这一代游戏机开发第二款游戏的工作室）现在能够更好地优化他们的 S 系列项目。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-is-no-longer-making-new-games-for-the-xbox-one-174452073.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-is-no-longer-making-new-games-for-the-xbox-one-174452073.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 43f1d8e3-1081-487c-9e75-c2b078226b2e</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:44:52 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686851120</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T17:45:33+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/dbc5d640-0ba1-11ee-9cfa-3edbf2e9c282" width="4928"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/dbc5d640-0ba1-11ee-9cfa-3edbf2e9c282" width="4928"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Anadolu Agency via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[MERSIN, TURKEY - AUGUST 11: Gamepads and Microsoft Xbox One gaming console are seen in Mersin, Turkey, on August 11, 2019. (Photo by Sezgin Pancar/Anadolu Agency/Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Gaming console]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Live Nation and Ticketmaster to start showing hidden ticket costs]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>当您以 30 美元的价格购买一张音乐会门票时，这绝非有趣，只是在经过一系列无休止的无定形费用后才发现它实际上是它的三倍。几十年来，这一直是消费者反抗像 Ticketmaster 这样的公司的核心，现在情况可能正在发生变化。</p><p> Ticketmaster 和 Live Nation 承诺在美国消费者购买前向他们提供实际的票价，而不是他们用来吸引顾客的仙境价格。预计拜登总统将在今天下午晚些时候与现场娱乐行业领袖会面时正式宣布此举，<ins> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAc7aWmUD6H2kuTzyL8gKS2nof0XhyQBdCy8xnwSrEZRf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fticketmaster-seatgeek-to-show-ticket-buyers-all-in-pricing-that-includes-fees-7c66f039" class="rapid-with-clickid">正如最初报道的那样</a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAc7aWmUD6H2kuTzyL8gKS2nof0XhyQBdCy8xnwSrEZRf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fticketmaster-seatgeek-to-show-ticket-buyers-all-in-pricing-that-includes-fees-7c66f039" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>华尔街日报。</em></a></ins></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>自从宣布将向公司施加压力以<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.npr.org/2023/02/07/1155313067/biden-bill-stop-junk-fees-travel-entertainment-state-of-the-union-2023">消除隐藏费用和附加费</a></ins>在 2 月的国情咨文演讲中。由 Live Nation 和 Ticketmaster 合并而成的公司 Live Nation Entertainment 已正式承诺在 9 月之前进行这些透明度更改。</p><p>尽管 Live Nation/Ticketmaster 已承诺改变，承诺“明确的总价”，但拜登今天晚些时候在白宫主持了一场圆桌讨论会，以鼓励 SeatGeek、Airbnb、DICE 等其他公司也这样做.预计大多数参加圆桌会议的公司将对消费者透明度做出某种承诺。 Airbnb 在这方面对消费者特别不友好，收取所有那些神秘的清洁费，但开始<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airbnb-improved-price-transparency-152910440.html">解决透明度问题</a></ins>去年年底。</p><p> “今天的自愿行动表明，无论大小，公司都认识到为消费者提供诚实、预先总价的重要性，而不是在结账结束时以意外费用来欺骗他们。这也只是解决经济中垃圾收费问题的第一步，”<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/06/15/president-biden-recognizes-actions-by-private-sector-ticketing-and-travel-companies-to-eliminate-hidden-junk-fees-and-provide-millions-of-customers-with-transparent-pricing/">白宫在一份声明中说。</a></ins></p><p>虽然这些变化并没有消除垃圾费用（公司将成为公司），但它们确实为消费者提供了重要信息，使他们能够做出明智的购买决定，这是一个开始。早在二月份，拜登就提出了立法<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/02/01/fact-sheet-president-biden-highlights-new-progress-on-his-competition-agenda/">称为垃圾费保护法</a></ins>实际减少这些隐藏费用的存在，包括购买音乐会和体育赛事数字门票时的超额费用。参议员 Richard Blumenthal (D-CT) 和 Sheldon Whitehouse (D-RI) 在国会提出了类似的立法，但尚未付诸表决。</p><p> Ticketmaster 在销售 Taylor Swift 的“时代”巡演门票时遇到一系列问题，导致客户遇到网站中断、大量机器人程序和极端等待时间，最近遭到抨击。由于没有足够的供应来满足需求，该公司最终完全取消了此次销售。这<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ticketmaster-live-nation-senate-judiciary-hearing-195504179.html">导致参议院举行听证会，</a>讨论该公司的垄断行为。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/live-nation-and-ticketmaster-to-start-showing-hidden-ticket-costs-170552346.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/live-nation-and-ticketmaster-to-start-showing-hidden-ticket-costs-170552346.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4fe99fc0-0339-4e55-a3af-3ab1cc4244cf</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 17:05:52 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686848102</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T16:55:07+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="3456" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4c50a740-0b99-11ee-aff7-466417ec1e03" width="5184"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3456" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4c50a740-0b99-11ee-aff7-466417ec1e03" width="5184"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_htm